Subject: Invalid Client Secret is provided
Description:
It appears that our client secret with the Azure Active Directory has expired and the system didn't warn us until after this happened. We have created a new secret but we have no option to add the new one to the Endpoint Synchronization settings.

This is preventing us from adding new users to the system and causing risks to data leakage.
Solution_Comment__c: Resolved after pointing to the correct steps from the User Manual.
